TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select batchid as BATCHID, prestagepositionseq as PRESTAGEPOSITIONSEQ from tenantname_dicl_prestageposition where batchname in (select distinct aud.sapcimportbatchname as sapcimportbatchname from tenantname_dicl_audit aud join tenantname_dicl_purge_control pur on aud.processname = pur.processname and aud.sourcesystem = pur.sourcesystem where aud.sapcstagetablename = 'CS_STAGEPOSITION' and aud.statusflag in (2, 3) and pur.stagemirrorpurge = 1 and (sysdate - pur.stagemirrorretaindays) >= aud.statusdatetime)
